rxiv-maker (1.6.2-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix Google Colab compatibility - handle ensurepip failures
  * Improve virtual environment creation in restricted environments
  * Add fallback pip installation via get-pip.py
  * Enhanced error handling for uv installation
  * Support Python 3.10+ for Ubuntu 22.04 compatibility
  * Robust dependency installation with multiple fallback methods

 -- Ricardo Henriques <ricardo@henriqueslab.org>  Thu, 29 Aug 2025 15:30:00 +0000

rxiv-maker (1.5.18-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix Ubuntu 24.04 dependency compatibility
  * Updated python3-matplotlib requirement: ≥3.7.0 → ≥3.6.0
  * Updated python3-pypdf requirement: ≥6.0.0 → ≥4.0.0
  * Added missing dependency: python3-crossrefapi
  * Automated LaTeX article generation with modern CLI
  * Figure creation capabilities with Python/R integration
  * DOI validation and bibliography management
  * Cross-platform compatibility with Docker/Podman support
  * Comprehensive validation and error handling
  * Rich CLI output formatting and progress indicators

 -- Rxiv-Maker Contributors <rxiv.maker@gmail.com>  Thu, 15 Aug 2025 12:00:00 +0000
